QuestData.Title: Furious Fowl
QuestData.Description: So these guys like fish, huh? Well how about we finish what you started and make them LOVE us?$b$bI've still got some explosive powder from the wreck, just need something to attract the fish.$b$bGuts is sure to do the trick - never fails. I saw some birds flyin' around south of town.$b$bWell? Whatcha waitin' for?
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect 6 Fistfuls of Bird Guts from Bloodtalons in Dookin' Grounds.
